   <section class="main"> 
    <div class="wrapper"> 
     <h1 class="main-header">The Power of Optimism</h1> 
     <p class="sub-header">There are people who believe anything is possible–and frequently prove it. At UCLA, we call this optimism and we call ourselves optimists. We are a public university; we were created to serve. So this site is for you too. And all optimists everywhere. Because it has never been just about us. It has always been about we.</p> 
